 * Description: This method lists files from a specified URI in an S3 bucket.
 * It uses the AWS S3 SDK to make requests to the S3 service. The method is
 * designed to handle large numbers of files by using pagination and continuation
 * tokens. It also supports recursive listing of files within a directory.
